data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom property in the desirable Barry Farms neighborhood of Washington, D.C. This 3-level Federal-style home offers a comfortable and convenient living experience.  Located within close proximity to the Metro, residents will enjoy easy access to public transportation, making commuting a breeze. Additionally, the neighborhood boasts an array of restaurants, shops, and amenities within walking distance, ensuring you'll never run out of things to do. Don't forget the proximity to the Navy Yard!  Sports enthusiasts will be delighted to find Nationals Stadium and Audi Field just a short distance away, allowing for easy access to thrilling games and events. Whether you're a baseball or soccer fan, or simply enjoy the lively atmosphere of the stadium, you'll have endless entertainment options at your fingertips.  The inside of this home is thoughtfully designed with modern features and an open layout. The stainless steel appliances in the kitchen add a touch of elegance and functionality, while the in-unit washer and dryer provide convenience and efficiency. With a spacious and long back yard, you can relax and unwind while enjoying the outdoors.  The property also offers a good-sized yard, perfect for outdoor activities or simply soaking up the sunshine. For residents with a car, on-street parking isavailabley.  This home is ideal for those seeking a quiet, clean, and comfortable living environment, with easy access to public transportation, nearby amenities, and exciting entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your next home.  Available immediately.
